        <div class="text span-5 last">
        <h4> <a href="https://www.thejournal.ie/readme/travellers-coronavirus-5113397-Jun2020/">Opinion: 'Conditions for Travellers have been difficult in the Covid-19 shutdown'</a></h4>
                    <div class="metadata">
                <span class="date">
                                        Jun 6th 2020, 1:00 PM                </span>
                <span class="views">
                    <span class="red-views icon iconViewVeryPopular"></span>39,731 Views                </span>
                <a href="https://www.thejournal.ie/readme/travellers-coronavirus-5113397-Jun2020/#comments" title="Comment on Opinion: 'Conditions for Travellers have been difficult in the Covid-19 shutdown'">
                    <span class="icon iconComment"></span> No Comments                </a>
            </div>
                <p class="excerpt excerpt_holder">
                Bernard Joyce of the Irish Traveller Movement says more needs to be done to protect Travellers during this pandemic and beyond.        </p>
